    <title>Vue3 源码阅读笔记（五）—— diff 算法解析</title>
    <link href="http://www.bebopser.com/2020/12/20/vue3source5/"/>
    <id>http://www.bebopser.com/2020/12/20/vue3source5/</id>
    <published>2020-12-20T03:20:44.000Z</published>
